1
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:17,440
♪In the airport lounge
at the break of day♪

2
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:22,240
♪A page of dust beneath my fingers♪

3
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:25,160
♪Filled with stories♪

4
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,280
♪That others never got to tell♪

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,960
♪We stand where the law draws its line♪

6
00:00:33,040 --> 00:00:35,600
♪One foot in homeland,
one foot in another land♪

7
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:37,160
♪With every single stamp we bring down♪

8
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:40,040
♪The world is split an inch wider♪

9
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:42,600
♪Raise your eyes, face the light♪

10
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:45,080
♪See the truth, and see the fright♪

11
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,800
♪Guard the crack within this door♪

12
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:52,600
♪Keep the way back home
always burning bright♪

13
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:57,040
♪The camera pans
across the boarding crowd♪

14
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:59,200
♪Some wear a smile,
some have their eyes adrift♪

15
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,440
♪A red suitcase♪

16
00:01:01,440 --> 00:01:05,360
♪Tied with faded pasts
and broken prayers♪

17
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:09,360
♪We stand where the law draws its line♪

18
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:12,080
♪One foot in homeland,
one foot in another land♪

19
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,960
♪With every single stamp we bring down♪

20
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:17,400
♪It's the heartbeat
echoing the call of law♪

21
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:30,000
[Gimlet Eyes]

22
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:32,960
[Episode 22]

23
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,490
Here, take it.

24
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:47,660
Qian Shengkai.

25
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,410
Binjiang City Plaza.

26
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,820
Same place.

27
00:01:51,230 --> 00:01:52,290
The photo was cropped.

28
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:54,050
These two photos were taken
by the same person

29
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:55,100
at the same location.

30
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,850
He was taking pictures
of the little girl

31
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:57,820
and spotted Qian Shengkai.

32
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:58,980
So he turned around,

33
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,130
moved closer, and took another shot.

34
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,380
It's him.

35
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,850
Put it back.

36
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:18,290
Found it!

37
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,220
I left it on top of the cabinet.

38
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,690
Here, take a look.

39
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,410
Sure.

40
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,170
That's…

41
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,450
That's you!

42
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,100
This one

43
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,980
was taken when Cong was 16.

44
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,780
I think he used

45
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,730
an FM10 with manual focus.

46
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,890
That was a gift I bought for myself,

47
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,170
my first 135 film camera.

48
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,010
Later, I gave it to Cong.

49
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:46,660
Cong.

50
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,540
Cong!

51
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,220
You still have that camera, right?

52
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,220
Of course, I still have it.

53
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,500
Back then, Cong was shy.

54
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,850
He wouldn't photograph strangers,

55
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,780
so I posed for him.

56
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,820
We shot all day.

57
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,940
These really are great shots.

58
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,730
Better than mine.

59
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,380
This one.

60
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:06,100
This one.

61
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,010
This one's my favorite.

62
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,380
Candid shot by Cong.

63
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:10,730
Candid shot?

64
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:13,820
Cong?

65
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,380
What's wrong?

66
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,570
Why are you so quiet?

67
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:19,940
Not feeling well?

68
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:23,780
He was arguing with me

69
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,890
the whole way here.

70
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,220
Probably got a headache now.

71
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,380
Yeah, a headache.

72
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:32,220
Then go home and get some rest.

73
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,730
I'm here whenever you want to visit.

74
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,940
I'll dig up some more photos,

75
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,260
and you can check them out next time.

76
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:38,660
Alright then.

77
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,940
I'll take this with me, Mr. Xiang.

78
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,410
Go ahead.

79
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,340
Go home and get some rest.

80
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:41,980
Sure.

81
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:43,130
Take care, Mr. Xiang.

82
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:43,820
Alright.

83
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,410
Take some medicine when you get home.

84
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,820
And get some rest.

85
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:48,340
Sir, are you taking my picture?

86
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,140
I am.

87
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,140
Thank you!

88
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:50,930
You're welcome.

89
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,810
Beautiful.

90
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,340
Here, can you blow the bubbles this way?

91
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,410
Nice.

92
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,700
One more!

93
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,370
I'm gonna switch cameras.

94
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:19,050
Awesome.

95
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,040
[Urgent Investigation Brief
Qian Shengkai, 35. Family Man.]

96
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:18,900
Cong.

97
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,730
How sure are you?

98
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,340
Right now, we can at least confirm

99
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,730
that both photos
were taken by Xiang Xiuyuan.

100
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,410
But that alone

101
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,020
isn't enough to prove

102
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,700
that he gave these photos to Du Li

103
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,370
or that he was ever

104
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,460
involved in smuggling.

105
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,140
Mr. Shen.

106
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,490
I'm requesting approval
to investigate Xiang Xiuyuan's company.

107
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:52,370
Approved.

108
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:57,960
[To my dearest Dad, Happy Father's Day!
Love, Guo Cong, 2000]

109
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:29,560
[Xiangliang]

110
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:50,030
[China Customs]

111
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:50,700
Cong.

112
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,300
Xiangliang Company's books
for the past 15 years

113
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:54,180
are clean.

114
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,340
A few transactions from 15 years ago

115
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:56,940
are murky.

116
00:08:59,030 --> 00:08:59,980
What about Xiang Xiuyuan?

117
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:01,650
What's his explanation?

118
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,530
Xiang Xiuyuan said

119
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,770
the company's operations

120
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,580
were mainly handled by your father.

121
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,180
He once suspected your father
of smuggling,

122
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,770
but he had no proof.

123
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,340
Later,

124
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,060
after your father passed away,

125
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,820
he stopped looking into it.

126
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,340
Guo Cong.

127
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:25,530
Don't put too much on yourself.

128
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,370
It's just Xiang Xiuyuan's
side of the story.

129
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,940
We'll keep digging.

130
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:34,530
However, we're talking
about over a decade ago.

131
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,890
It's going

132
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,530
to take some time to sort it all out.

133
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:56,850
Looks like

134
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,100
everyone knows, right?

135
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,060
And you're smiling?

136
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,490
What am I supposed to do? Cry?

137
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,220
What did the leaders say?

138
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,060
Given what's happened,

139
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,940
I definitely have to step aside.

140
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,220
I already applied for leave.

141
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,700
While I'm away,

142
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:14,940
it's on you.

143
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,220
There's not much else to say.

144
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,720
A holiday is just around the corner.

145
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,180
Cases tend to spike.

146
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,460
We still have to hold

147
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:26,980
the line at the border.

148
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,610
I'll go get changed.

149
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:30,010
All the plating here
is Uncle Xiang's work.

150
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:31,250
Look at the colors,

151
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:33,180
the arrangement,
and the balance of meat and veggies.

152
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:43,340
I'll transfer the money to you
on WeChat later.

153
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,220
Sure.

154
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,300
- Take care. - Thanks.

155
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,770
I'll be back late tonight.

156
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,820
What you said before
might actually be happening.

157
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:06,370
Which part? You're being so cryptic.

158
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,180
It's about Guo Cong.
I'm a little worried about him.

159
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:12,490
Oh, so you finally admit
you're worried about him.

160
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:13,980
I'll tell you when I get back.

161
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:29,280
[Xiangliang 15115]

162
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:44,000
[Fishing Vessel 15022]

163
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,050
Xiaoyan, what's up?

164
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,730
Aren't you guys
about to start your shift?

165
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:30,810
Mr. Guo, Zhang Yu is missing.

166
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,090
Yeah, we're about to go on duty,

167
00:17:32,110 --> 00:17:32,900
but she still hasn't come back.

168
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:33,860
Where did she go?

169
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,570
I don't know.

170
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:35,900
She came back to the dorm

171
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,900
and seemed really off yesterday.

172
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,810
She kept going on about you.

173
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,700
She went out after dinner

174
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,660
and hasn't been back since.

175
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:42,180
Her phone's off. She's not answering.

176
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,730
Did she say where she was going?

177
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,380
No.

178
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:44,940
Listen,

179
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:45,810
Cong,

180
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:46,770
we're calling the police right now.

181
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,220
Let the office know.

182
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,090
I'm on my way.

183
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:50,050
Hanging up.

184
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:50,860
Got it.

185
00:18:01,270 --> 00:18:01,940
Shihuo.

186
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,700
Zhang Yu drove Xiaoyan's car last night.

187
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:05,140
She's sending you the GPS history now.

188
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,090
Got it.

189
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:12,730
Shihuo,

190
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,180
send this GPS data

191
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,250
to the police and Customs.

192
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,620
Zhang Yu stopped at two places.

193
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,010
Xiangliang Company

194
00:18:18,030 --> 00:18:19,010
and the dock.

195
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,180
I'm heading to the dock now.

196
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:21,700
Got it.

197
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,460
Be careful.

198
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,290
Having fun yet?

199
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,570
Relax.

200
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,140
It'll all be over soon.

