207
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:05,570
You okay?

208
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,810
Xiang Xiuyuan.

209
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,490
Xiang Xiuyuan.

210
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,900
Xiang Xiuyuan.

211
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:12,940
There are

212
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:15,460
two crates at the bow
with bodies inside.

213
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,660
One of them should be Long Shuo.

214
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:18,730
Can you move?

215
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:19,250
Yes.

216
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:26,280
[Xiangliang]

217
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:31,490
Cong.

218
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,570
So you came after all.

219
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,090
Why did you do all this?

220
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:44,860
Come on,

221
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,460
have a drink with me.

222
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,620
It might be our last chance.

223
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,770
Let go of me!

224
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:58,570
The rope!

225
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,220
Let go!

226
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,570
Let go of me!

227
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,530
No signal!

228
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:24,660
Up there.

229
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,010
Might get a signal up there.

230
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:27,220
Go!

231
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:28,290
I've got him.

232
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,090
Let go of me!

233
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,620
Let go!

234
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,090
Tell me,

235
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,250
if my mentor hadn't shown up,

236
00:22:58,790 --> 00:22:59,980
what were you planning to do with me?

237
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:02,050
The ocean would be
where you ended up.

238
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,700
I just hadn't decided

239
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:07,330
which corpse I'd tie you to.

240
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:11,810
Did you call the police?

241
00:23:12,070 --> 00:23:13,050
Anti-smuggling is on the way.

242
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:17,700
Cong.

243
00:23:19,030 --> 00:23:20,250
Look at that photo.

244
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:23,420
You were only 13.

245
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:24,900
That was your first time

246
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:27,090
going out to sea
with your father and me.

247
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,140
You got terribly seasick.

248
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,290
After that photo was taken,

249
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:33,220
you lay right here
until we got back to shore.

250
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:35,330
After that,

251
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:36,810
you hardly ever came out to sea
with me again.

252
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:38,530
My father died out here!

253
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,460
How could I not care?

254
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:47,220
Now you can tell me the truth,
can't you?

255
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:49,330
Fine.

256
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:52,050
Ask me.

257
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:53,980
I'll tell you everything.

258
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:56,620
When did you start smuggling?

259
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,530
2008.

260
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,290
That was the third year

261
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:04,140
after your father
and I started Xiangliang Company.

262
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,090
The financial crisis hit.

263
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:10,330
I tried everything I could

264
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,330
to keep the company alive.

265
00:24:15,160 --> 00:24:17,250
In the end,
smuggling was my only way out.

266
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:19,940
That money kept the company afloat.

267
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:22,940
That same year,

268
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,330
I met Sa Ziyi.

269
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:26,730
But

270
00:24:28,070 --> 00:24:29,770
whether it was with Sa Ziyi

271
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:32,810
or later with Du Li,

272
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:35,050
I never got involved
in the actual smuggling.

273
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:38,290
I only picked people
to be used as mules.

274
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,860
Through those photos?

275
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:40,900
That's right.

276
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:43,090
What about Sa Ziyi and those dolls?

277
00:24:43,510 --> 00:24:45,420
I planted all those dolls.

278
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,530
You planted them?

279
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:47,250
Yes.

280
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:49,570
Weren't you working with Sa Ziyi?

281
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:52,180
Because I have my own rules.

282
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:55,460
I never allowed Sa Ziyi to touch drugs.

283
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:57,940
But in the end,

284
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:00,290
she was stupid enough
to use kids to move drugs.

285
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:03,140
Principles?
After everything you've done?

286
00:25:03,350 --> 00:25:03,980
Of course!

287
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,730
I have my own bottom line!

288
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,420
You killed Sa Ziyi!

289
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:09,490
And you still didn't stop!

290
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:11,810
Why did you go to Du Li?

291
00:25:15,510 --> 00:25:16,730
By then,

292
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,810
I had been addicted

293
00:25:20,310 --> 00:25:22,700
to finding people with cracks in them.

294
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:26,770
Watching them choose
to become mules themselves.

295
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:29,090
That kind of thrill…

296
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:31,700
How could I possibly stop?

297
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:32,700
So,

298
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,700
you're Mr. E?

299
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:36,980
What do you think?

300
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,460
You killed Du Li.

301
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:42,620
And you'd just find someone else,

302
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:43,730
right?

303
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,250
Honestly,

304
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,140
I haven't decided yet.

305
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,770
I think I'm getting tired.

306
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:57,810
Tired.

307
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:05,940
Cong.

308
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:09,220
Cong, can you get me some water?

309
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:11,860
I'm begging you.

310
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:15,180
Just let me have some water, Cong.

311
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,090
Cong.

312
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:16,900
Stop!

313
00:26:27,510 --> 00:26:28,250
Let her go!

314
00:26:28,350 --> 00:26:29,330
Stay back!

315
00:26:32,030 --> 00:26:32,660
Get out!

316
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,660
Out!

317
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:37,140
Move to the bow!

318
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,250
Uncle Xiang, let her go.

319
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,180
Get out!

320
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:39,530
Okay!

321
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,530
I'm moving!

322
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:45,620
Get to the bow!

323
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:47,660
Get out!

324
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,180
Why were you trying to kill me?

325
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:59,180
Why?

326
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,330
You turned yourselves into animals.

327
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:04,050
Why turn me into one, too?

328
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:08,290
Why force me to become a killer, too?

329
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,330
I am

330
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:13,810
a decent man.

331
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:16,090
A man with principles!

332
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,090
You can't hold that line.

333
00:27:18,110 --> 00:27:19,490
No matter how long you try,
you can't hold it.

334
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,250
If you'd just played by my rules,

335
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:22,980
you'd all still be alive.

336
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:23,980
Du Li would be alive.

337
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:25,460
Sa Ziyi would be alive.

338
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,530
Not just you.

339
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:27,330
Cong can't either.

340
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:28,570
And that trainee of his.

341
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:30,220
None of you can.

342
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,090
Wouldn't it

343
00:27:31,110 --> 00:27:32,620
be better if you just lived
your damn lives?

344
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:34,770
Why did you want me dead so badly?

345
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:35,900
Guo Cong

346
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,620
won't end up like you.

347
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:40,940
I'll save him from Customs.

348
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:44,490
I'll make sure he gets a different life.

349
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:47,290
Please…

350
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,940
don't…

351
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:59,140
Don't…

352
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,380
Goodbye,

353
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,810
old friend.

354
00:28:32,270 --> 00:28:34,090
- Xiang Xiuyuan. - Come any closer,

355
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:35,940
and I'll kill her!

356
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:37,940
Back off!

357
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:38,900
Farther!

358
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:42,250
I just want to talk with you!

359
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,770
You think you can decide
Guo Cong's life?

360
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:47,940
Guo Cong,

361
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,810
I raised you for 15 years!

362
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:53,090
I watched you grow up!

363
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:56,090
How could Chen Sanhe just show up,

364
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:57,530
keep you at Customs,

365
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:58,940
and put you in harm's way?

366
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:01,290
That was his choice!

367
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:03,010
He had to pay the price!

368
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:06,940
Guo Cong!

369
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,620
I want you to know

370
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:12,730
no one in this world
cares about you more than I do!

371
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:13,940
You call that caring?

372
00:29:14,750 --> 00:29:16,330
Weren't you just trying to kill me?

373
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,940
I never wanted to kill anyone!

374
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:19,290
I never wanted any of this!

375
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:21,330
They forced my hand!

376
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,860
Sa Ziyi is dead.

377
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:27,050
Du Li is dead.

378
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:28,860
Long Shuo is dead.

379
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,530
Xiao Dabao is dead.

380
00:29:31,110 --> 00:29:32,010
Everyone who knew

381
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:34,220
who I was is gone.

382
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:37,730
This could've all been over.

383
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:38,980
You!

384
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:41,250
And you!

385
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:45,330
Why did you force me to choose?

386
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:47,290
What choice did I have?

387
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:53,180
You must be sentimental.

388
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,380
It's been 20 years,

389
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:57,570
and this place looks exactly the same.

390
00:29:57,590 --> 00:29:59,730
Mr. Xiang cares so much about Mr. Guo.

391
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:00,730
If you didn't know better,

392
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:02,140
you'd think he was Mr. Guo's father.

393
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,620
And Guo Shuliang.

394
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:11,770
The first person you killed
was Guo Shuliang!

395
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:17,330
What did you say?

396
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:21,530
Cong.

397
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,090
Cong…

398
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:24,290
That was just

399
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,420
an accident.

400
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,660
It was an accident.

401
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:27,810
Shuliang.

402
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:28,730
Xiang,

403
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:29,940
this is smuggling.

404
00:30:30,110 --> 00:30:30,940
It's a crime.

405
00:30:31,310 --> 00:30:32,730
And drugs kill people!

406
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,660
Give it to me.

407
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,700
It's my first time doing this.

408
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,090
I'll never touch it again, okay?

409
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:36,860
Not even once.

410
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:37,940
Turn it in to the police now.

411
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:38,770
There's still time.

412
00:30:38,790 --> 00:30:40,490
Shuliang, think about your wife.

413
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,730
Think about Cong.

414
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,010
He's still just a kid.

415
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,420
They need us to make money

416
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,940
so they can live a better life.

417
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,530
A better life from this?

418
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:49,140
My family wants no part of that!

419
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,730
Give it back!

420
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:51,730
Give it to me!

421
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:53,900
Shuliang!

422
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:56,380
Don't tear it open, Shuliang!

423
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:58,250
That's all the money we have!

424
00:30:58,270 --> 00:30:59,770
Don't throw it away!

425
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,050
I'm trying to save you!

426
00:31:01,510 --> 00:31:02,490
Shuliang!

427
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,290
Move!

428
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:07,380
Shuliang!

429
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,330
I never expected

430
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:14,220
he'd find the drugs I hid!

431
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:16,980
And I never imagined
he'd fall overboard!

432
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,420
Dad…

433
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,860
Dad…

434
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,570
If you hadn't started smuggling,

435
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:33,220
and if you'd listened to my father

436
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,940
and turned in the drugs,

437
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:37,220
none of this would have happened!

438
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:39,250
Have you ever thought about that?

439
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:42,460
I never touched drugs again
after that day!

440
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:45,330
I wasn't even involved
in the smuggling myself anymore!

441
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:47,730
Stop fooling yourself, Xiang Xiuyuan.

442
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,770
You were the most critical part

443
00:31:49,790 --> 00:31:50,940
of that smuggling ring!

444
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:53,770
You picked those mules one by one.

445
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:55,140
Every time you found one,

446
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,660
you forgave yourself a little more

447
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,220
because you wanted to believe

448
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,380
everyone was just like you,

449
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,050
ready to give in to temptation.

450
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:02,810
I'm telling you,

451
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:03,700
they're not!

452
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,010
Don't act like you're some kind of god.

453
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,570
You're nothing

454
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,380
but the first mule you ever chose,

455
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,700
and that choice
got Guo Cong's father killed!

456
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:13,860
That's the choice you could never

457
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:15,380
forgive yourself for!

458
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:18,620
Everything you've done
goes back to that!

459
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:19,290
No!

460
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,380
Everything I've done

461
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,420
was to give Guo Cong a better life.

462
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,860
It was all for you, Guo Cong.

463
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,860
I don't want that from you!

464
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:30,050
I want my father!

465
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:32,570
My own father!

466
00:32:32,590 --> 00:32:34,570
Do you understand that?

467
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,330
Cong.

468
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:39,290
I'm sorry.

469
00:32:39,350 --> 00:32:41,420
I'm so sorry.

470
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:43,010
There are too many people

471
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:45,220
you owe an apology to!

472
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,980
You owe my mentor!

473
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:50,380
My father!

474
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,570
Deng!

475
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,490
Qian!

476
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:53,860
Shen Taotao!

477
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:54,700
And you owe

478
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:57,140
every single mule you dragged into this!

479
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:59,420
This is all your fault!

480
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:01,730
I'm telling you, Xiang Xiuyuan.

481
00:33:02,030 --> 00:33:03,660
You will never

482
00:33:03,750 --> 00:33:06,220
ever replace Guo Cong's father!

483
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:14,330
Shut up!

484
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:19,900
Zhang Yu.

485
00:33:20,030 --> 00:33:20,420
Zhang Yu.

486
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,040
Zhang Yu.

487
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:22,810
Stop.

488
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,250
It's okay, Mentor.

489
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,380
Zhang Yu.

490
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:28,900
You're right!

491
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:31,490
Everything you said was right!

492
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,730
I lost.

493
00:33:34,310 --> 00:33:35,330
You win!

494
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,770
Guo Cong…

495
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:40,700
Fifteen years…

496
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:42,620
Your father's death

497
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:47,380
has been sitting on my chest
like a stone!

498
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:50,380
I could barely breathe!

499
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:52,980
Right now, it's just the three of us!

500
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,620
None of us is leaving!

501
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:56,860
We die together!

502
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:59,380
Sa Ziyi

503
00:33:59,830 --> 00:34:01,460
had no choice.

504
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:03,700
Du Li had no choice.

505
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,770
Long Shuo had no choice.

506
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,730
Xiao Dabao had no choice.

507
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:10,900
And neither do you!

508
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:13,900
Zhang Yu.

509
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,420
Everyone dies today.

510
00:34:28,480 --> 00:34:29,740
All of you die!

511
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:31,980
Go to hell!

512
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,780
Just die!

513
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:39,300
None of you gets to live!

514
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:44,690
You idiots should've
just played by my rules!

515
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:48,380
He's going to ram the boat!

516
00:34:58,070 --> 00:35:00,010
Move, Zhang Yu! Go!

517
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,300
Zhang Yu!

518
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:05,420
Steer the boat!

519
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:16,650
I…

520
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,050
I don't know how to do this!

521
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:19,570
Disengage autopilot!

522
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:31,610
I don't know how…

523
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,010
Let go of me!

524
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,340
- Let go! - Zhang Yu!

525
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,380
Hurry!

526
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:50,340
The wheel isn't working, Mentor!

527
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:14,690
Mentor.

528
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,130
The boat stopped.

529
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:38,340
Xiangliang 15115,

530
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:40,490
please follow the coast guard vessel
back to port.

531
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,130
Cong.

532
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:46,170
You won.

533
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:48,690
I lost.

534
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,650
This was never a war
between the two of us.

535
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,130
You're too naive.

536
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:58,090
The darkness in human nature
never goes away.

537
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,690
You really think you can hold the line?

538
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,380
You've been wrong all along.

539
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:06,530
The meaning of holding the line

540
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:07,940
is to keep holding.

541
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:10,210
As long as the border stands,

542
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:11,940
we'll be there guarding it.

543
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,340
And as long as we're there,

544
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,130
the people can rest easy.

545
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,530
Of course,

546
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:19,130
there will always be people

547
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:20,460
who push their luck,

548
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,860
and some will slip through.

549
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,170
But as long as we're there,

550
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,260
we'll bring them all to justice.

551
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:30,170
I've always remembered something
Guo Cong once said.

552
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:32,820
No one's perfect.

553
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:34,820
Everyone has cracks
in their personality.

554
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:36,860
There will always be people

555
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:39,900
trying to stuff darkness into them.

556
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,570
What we need to do

557
00:37:42,190 --> 00:37:44,090
is be the ones
who shine light into them.

558
00:37:48,110 --> 00:37:50,490
It's getting dark.

559
00:37:52,230 --> 00:37:53,170
Dark.

560
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:16,800
[Mainland Fishing Vessel Loading Point]

561
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:14,170
Section I…

562
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,090
people will leave,

563
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:18,210
and new ones will come.

564
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:21,170
But Passenger Inspection Section I
will always be here.

565
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:24,210
The border
will always need someone watching it.

566
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:58,760
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

567
00:39:59,680 --> 00:40:06,400
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

568
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:09,520
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

569
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:11,980
If you want to become a true guardian
